317	- Edit profile button: 48dp minimum height
318	- Avatar: 80dp diameter (decorative, no interaction beyond visual)
319	- All interactive elements meet 48dp minimum touch target
320	
321	### Screen Reader Support
322	
323	- `AnnounceRouteChange` for tab switches
324	- Live region on profile name: "Profile screen, ${userName}"
325	
326	---
327	
328	## 11. Anti-Patterns
329	
330	**Do Not:**
331	- Add a FAB to Profile tab screen (tab screens don't have FABs per UX.md)
332	- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list — use `SingleChildScrollView`)
333	- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only for content cards)
334	- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)
335	- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito
336	- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp
337	- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text
338	- Add more than the 4 defined sections (header, mindfulness, settings, about)
339	- Use hero animations (simple push navigation with no shared elements)
340	- Add elevation shadows beyond level1 for cards (soft shadow only)
341	- Place critical actions below the thumb zone
342	- Use hard-coded user name — derive from `UserPreferencesProvider.name`
343	
344	---
345	
346	## 12. Navigation Dependencies
347	
348	| Destination | Route | Navigation Type |
349	|---|---|---|
350	| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Push |
351	| Settings | `/settings` | Push |
352	
353	---
354	
355	## 13. Theme Dependencies
356	
357	This screen uses `Theme.of(context)` to access design tokens. The theme is configured via `app_theme.dart` which provides:
358	- `ColorScheme` with all palette colors mapped
359	- `TextTheme` with Nunito font family
360	- `CardTheme` with proper corner radius and elevation
